      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "## 5.2.0\n\n- 个人知识库同步现支持文件夹层级结构——子文件夹中的笔记会保留原始目录树，不再全部堆在根目录下（感谢 @changliu1990 的 PR）\n\n\n## What's Changed\n* fix: sync knowledge base folders recursively by @changliu1990 in https://github.com/chenxiccc/obsidian-ima.copilot-sync/pull/1\n\n## New Contributors\n* @changliu1990 made their first contribution in https://github.com/chenxiccc/obsidian-ima.copilot-sync/pull/1\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/chenxiccc/obsidian-ima.copilot-sync/compare/5.1.0...5.2.0",
